LinguaCE is an open-source mobile application for learning the Chechen
language (нохчийн мотт) with AI assistance.

This product includes third-party open-source software:
  - Flutter & Dart (BSD-3-Clause) — https://flutter.dev
  - Supabase Flutter (MIT) — https://supabase.com
  - google_fonts (Apache-2.0)
  - flutter_markdown (BSD-3-Clause)
  - http (BSD-3-Clause)
  - shared_preferences (BSD-3-Clause)

The Chechen language content and the 1992 Latin transliteration system
("Muziŋ Dar") are provided for educational purposes.
